#########################
# Installation / Config #
#########################


1) backup shop and database

#####
2) copy files from "eshop" to your shop

#####	
3) Add the following module-entries in your configuration

	oxoutput => marm/piwik/marm_piwik_oxoutput

#####	
4) Set up your PIWIK variables in Master Settings > Core Settings > Piwik setup

	Piwik URL should be without piwik.php ending. like "www.example.org/piwik/"

#####
5) Clean your language cache (cleanup eShop tmp directory)


If you don't see Master Settings > Core Settings > Piwik setup tab, logout and login again to admin section.


